name: Predict_Loan_Deafult
additionalDescriptionForLLM: Use this model to predict whether or not a customer will default on their request loan. The value for the column named "proba_1.0" predicts the probability on a scale of 0.0 to 1.0 that the customer will default on the loan. You may need to convert the value of proba_1.0 to a percentage (0-100%) by multiplying it by 100 before returning it. A proba_1.0 value equal to 1.0 means a total certainty (100%) chance of the customer defaulting.
